*Dogovorili* smo da se sastanemo u parku u pet ujutru. (We agreed to meet in the park at 5 am.)

*Dogovorili* smo se da ćemo razgovarati o svemu posle večere. (We agreed to talk about everything after dinner.)

*Dogovorila* je da će biti tu u pet sati. (She agreed to be there at five o'clock.)

*Dogovorili* smo se da ćemo se vratiti za par dana. (We agreed to come back in a few days.)

*Dogovorilo* se da će se sve obaviti za jedan dan. (It was agreed that everything would be done in one day.)